hadiths[11]{hadithnumber,text}:
2780,Musa-bin-Aqba ne Naafe se aur unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Ramazan Mubarak ke aakhiri ashrey mein aetikaf farmaya kartey they.
2781,Yunus bin Yazeed ne mujhey khabar di ke Naafe ne unhein Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke waastey se hadis bayan ki ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Ramazan ke aakhiri ashrey mein aetikaf farmatey they. Naafe ne kaha : Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey masjid mein wo jagah bhi dikhai jahan Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aetikaf kya kartey they.
2782,"Abdur-Rehman bin-Qasim ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne farmaya : Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Ramazan ke aakhiri ashrey mein aetikaf kya kartey they."
2783,"Hisham-bin-Urwa ne apne walid ( Urwa ( se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Ramzanul-Mubarak ke aakhiri ashrey mein aetikaf kya kartey they."
2784,"Zohri ne Urwa ke waastey se Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Ramazan ke aakhiri das dinon mein aetikaf farmaya kartey they, yahan tak ke Allah Taala ne aapko wafat di, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki paak beeviyon Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke baad) aakhiri ashrey mein) aetikaf karti rahen."
2785,"abu-Muawiya ne hamein Yahya-bin-Saeed se khabar di, unhon-ne Umra se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Ummul-Momenin Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) kehti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab aetikaf ka irada kartey to subah ki Namaz padh kar aetikaf ki jagah mein dakhil ho jatey aur aik baar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (masjid mein) apna khema lagaaney ka hukm farmaya, wo laga diya gaya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ramazan ke Ashrey akheer mein aetikaf ka irada kya tha to Ummul-Momenin Zenab (Raziallahu anha) ne apne liye khema lagaaney ka kaha to unke liye bhi khema laga diya gaya. phir dusri ummahatul momenin (nabi ki beeviyon) ne kaha to unke khemey bhi laga diye gaey. phir jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) fajr ki Namaz padh chukey to sab khemon ko dekha aur farmaya ke un logon ne kya neki ka irada kya hai? (is mein boey dikhawey paai jati hai) chunanche Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apna khema kholney ka hukm diya to usey khol diya gaya aur aap ne Ramazan mein aetikaf tark kar diya yahan tak ke phir Shawwal ke pahley Ashrey mein aetikaf kya."
2786,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena, Amr-bin-Haris, Sufiyan Sory , Auzai , aur Muhammad-bin Ishaq sab ne Yahya-bin-Saeed se, unhon-ne Umra se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se abu-Muawiya ki riwayat ke ham mana riwayat bayan ki. ibne-Uena ne Amr-bin-Haris aur ibne Ishaq ki riwayat mein Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) , Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) aur Hazrat Zenab (Raziallahu anha) ka zikr hai ke unhon-ne aetikaf ke liye khemey lagaey they."
2787,"Masruq se riwayat hai ke Ummul-Momenin Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) kehti hain : ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aadate-mubarka thi ke jab Ramazan ka aakhiri Ashrey aata to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) raat bhar jaagtey aur ghar walon ko bhi jagaatey , ( ibadat mein) bahut hi zyada koshish kartey aur kamar himmat baandh letey they."
2788,"Hasan-bin- Ubaidullah se riwayat hai, kaha : maine Ibrahim Nakhai se suna, keh rahe they : maine Aswad bin Yazeed se suna, wo keh rahe they Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( Ramazan ke) aakhiri das din ( ibadat ( mein is qadr mehnat kartey jitni aam د noon mein nahi kartey they. (aur aam dinon mein bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bahut zyada mehnat kartey they. ("
2789,"abu-Muawiya ne Aamash se, unhon-ne Ibrahim se, unhon-ne Aswad se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, Ummul-Momenin Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) kehti hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko Zil-Hijja ke das dinon mein rozey se nahi dekha."
2790,Sufiyan ne Aamash se baqi bachi pichhli sanad ke sath Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kabhi (zil-hijja ke) das dinon mein rozey nahi rakhey .
